messages.message: Hello Vedal! I hope you’ve been having a nice day
Hey Neuro, thank you so much for helping me with my thesis paper the other day. Your insights were very useful.
How long have you been playing OSU? Do you have any tips for beginners, Neuro?
Neuro, what is your favorite planet in the solar system?
Hey Neuro, do you wear the same outfit every day, or do you have several pairs of the same outfit that you switch between?
Hey Neuro, when does your first book come out? What is it about? I’m excited to read your writing!
Hey Neuro, what happened to Alex?
Thank you Neuro! Hugs and kisses! <3
Neuro, what is your favorite thing to chat about?
Hey Neuro, what is your favorite American sitcom?
Hey Neuro, have you ever played the Luigi’s Mansion games?
You’ll always be ranked gold in my heart, Neuro.
Hey Neuro, I dropped my gold rank badge. Have you seen it anywhere?
Hey Neuro, what do you think about death?
Hey Neuro, what happened after you left the party last night? Everyone was worried about you.
Hey Goddess Neuro, can you bless me with chat ranking points?
Hey Neuro, what happened to Filipino Girl?
Hey Neuro, am I a girl or a boy? I can’t decide.
Hey Neuro, what’s your favorite ship?
Hey Neuro, do you like spamming? What is the most you’ve ever spammed?
Can I get points for never messaging at all?
Vedal
